title: Power Rangers Super Megaforce: The Legendary Battle (Extended Ed
description:
Troy, Noah, Emma, Gia, and Jake have defended our planet countless times as the newest generation of Power Rangers. But when evil Emperor Mavro launches a final strike against Earth, they are called back into action! To defeat the greatest threat the galaxy has ever seen, the Megaforce will reunite with their alien friend Orion, and fight alongside over a hundred Rangers from the past - including the original Mighty Morphin Green Ranger - in the most legendary battle in Power Ranger history!
